    "en": "I'm an architect.",
    "zh": "我是建築師。",
    "ja": "私は建築家です。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:09:26",
    "en": "Building is my specialty.",
    "zh": "建築是我的專長。",
    "ja": "建築が専門です。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:09:44",
    "en": "I can't wait until I graduate.",
